{
  "stem": "1530.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we March for two weeks to [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oelsk. ?] Then we took the train to Odessa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's already April 5th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on the road, trying to get to America, not to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw Hungarian kids going back with  their trains to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we said, that's not for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't-- you didn't want to look for your brother?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew that he wouldn't go back to Hungary either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, we were--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not until the war was over, and we were here for awhile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody could tell us anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, so we had this hearing, you know, with this American attache.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he got us on a boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was unbelievable how they treated us there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the food-- and-- and we started to learn English the second day, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had to order food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were with the captain in a beautiful dining room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were treated like officers, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of the officers was a Jewish fellow, Jack Berman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were standing on the bottom of the boat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He told this person of the ship, he says, you see that girl?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want that girl to stay at my table at the dining room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What girl was he pointing at?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chicha.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was never good looking, but she had some femininity, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she's the one who had all the--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brains.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the brains, you're telling me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the brains, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we were on that boat that was called the Brand Whitlock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I don't have to spell it for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were treated like queens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother-in-law spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not yet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Jack, Jack Berman--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
